Prometheus is a systems and service monitoring system. It collects metrics from configured targets at given intervals, evaluates rule expressions, 
displays the results, and can trigger alerts if some condition is observed to be true.

https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=7gW5pSM6dlU

->Prometheus is a s/w appn used for event monitoring and alerting
->it records realtime metrics in a time series db using http pull model

WHy use prometheus?
-> pull based model
-> actively scrapes targets to receive metrics 
endpoints defined in prometheus config
node and appn exporter will listen on particular port and prometheus intiates http call to particular exporter and fetch metrics 

free and opensource

https://github.com/prometheus
